      "content": "i get the monitoring thing but its such a hassle. if i'm already feeling 100% and my heart stuff is stable, isn't it basically just a matter of finding my new baseline? if i start the 2mg today, how long before my body adjusts to the new level? i just want to be sure i'm doing the right thing for my long term health.",
